:"2020-03-21T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bd78f2577a8449ed7f4242837b6df26b6e63de5","tid":1928774,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebcd546ca0c4a32f354cedfe96475312139c5a74","tid":1928774,"uid":103936,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"HR壓價係天性<br />\n尤其on9 會問你最低接受幾多<br />\n最後一定俾最底價你<br />\n<br />\n我結論係開實價唔開range<br />\nnever expect they will provide a better offer<br />\n冇得interview就算<br />\n有得in &gt; in完壓 &gt; 問佢覺得你有咩唔得 / 唔值呢個價<br />\na) 自身問題就將就下<br />\nb) 公司問題(eg 其他同事個價都係xxx)可以叫佢收皮<br />\nc) 假設問題(假設你能力未必做到xxx), <br />\n你可以反假設 過probation做到xxx 可唔可以guarantee 加返到你個價<br />\nor 反假設 唔到價 你唔開心 都係走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n企硬啦 輸俾HR 條數, 可能用一兩年加薪先追返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:00:20.000Z","msg":"agent hr 係掉轉喎<br />\n幫你扯高人工佢先多夾棍"},{"pid":"6b3a2a09b7a91e97d4bc41045aabf0dc8848fb08","tid":1928774,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1dd378cce81e10b8824f72d4addb8af91cfc102","tid":1928774,"uid":71508,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:39:45.000Z","msg":"你on9<br />\n你開高d咪得<br />\n有冇讀過mba架你<br />\n冇啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n你開20k<br />\n但你值15k<br />\n佢會壓<br />\n19<br />\n18<br />\n17<br />\n16<br />\n最後16k成交<br />\n你賺左<br />\n哈<br />\n7head"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:16:26.000Z","msg":"巴打好風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6873d5e862382823928984cc1cc76276a2248563","tid":1928774,"uid":288803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3da414dfe0a622c6ae716589c89ba766921795ea","tid":1928774,"uid":54486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:01:15.000Z","msg":"要睇你件貨難唔難搵，類似既貨值幾多<br />\n<br />\n人人賣$300，你開$400 有鬼人問，壓價都費事<br />\n<br />\n無晒貨得你有既，你叫$1000 都得添"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:18:55.000Z"